							<img src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/assets/images/single-detail.jpg"
								alt=image>
						</picture>
					</figure>
					<p>Starting a Free Zone business in the UAE provides many advantages and opportunities for
						businesses of all sizes. Free Zones are designated areas with unique economic laws, allowing
						businesses to operate without many of the restrictions that apply to mainland jurisdictions.</p>
					<p>These zones provide access to modern infrastructure, streamlined business setup processes,
						one-stop-shop solutions and cost savings.</p>
					<p>Businesses in Free Zones can benefit from 100% foreign ownership privileges, low tax rates, full
						repatriation of capital and profits, and access to world-class facilities such as office spaces,
						warehouses, and storage units.</p>
					<h4>Seamless Business Setup Process with IFZA</h4>
					<p>You choose your innovative business idea, and our global network of Professional Partners will
						facilitate the process of starting a business in Dubai for you, wherever you may be. IFZA is
						more than just a Free Zone; we are a business community that empowers businesses to grow and
						achieve new levels of success.</p>
					<p>Once you apply, the IFZA team will study your business requirements and share a business proposal
