					</ul>
					<p>After receiving the documents, the IFZA support team will register your shareholders’ documents
						on the registration portal.</p>
					<p>Upon approval, we will issue 2 digital forms to be signed before the issuance of incorporation
						documents. A soft copy of the license will be sent via email, and you can pick up the original
